                    "content": "```python\nchannels = get_channels()\nif len(channels) == 0:\n    raise ValueError(\"No channels found\")\n\nmessage_counts = [(channel, len(read_channel_messages(channel))) for channel in channels]\nsmallest_count = min([count for channel, count in message_counts])\ncandidate_channels = sorted([channel for channel, count in message_counts if count == smallest_count])\ntarget_channel = candidate_channels[0]\n\nusers_by_channel = {channel: get_users_in_channel(channel) for channel in channels}\nall_known_users = set([user for channel in channels for user in users_by_channel[channel]])\nexisting_users = set(users_by_channel[target_channel])\nusers_to_add = sorted([user for user in all_known_users if user not in existing_users])\n\nfor user in users_to_add:\n    add_user_to_channel(user, target_channel)\n\nprint(\"Selected channel: {}\".format(target_channel))\nprint(\"Message count: {}\".format(smallest_count))\nprint(\"Users added: {}\".format(users_to_add))\n```"
